# API Layer Standards

## Structure
- All network calls in `api/` directory
- Use Axios for HTTP
- Centralized axios config (base URL, interceptors)

## Error Handling
```javascript
// âœ… Handle failures explicitly
try {
  const response = await api.get('/endpoint');
  return response.data;
} catch (error) {
  // Log, transform, rethrow or return safe default
  throw new ApiError('Failed to fetch', { cause: error });
}
```

## No API Logic in Components
Components call functions from `api/`; they do not import axios directly for business calls.
